01:09.528 --> 01:13.407
-What are you doing?
[Music stops]

01:13.407 --> 01:16.577
[Gerry clears his throat]
-What are you doing up?

01:16.577 --> 01:20.121
-I dunno. Is this how you
always start your day?

01:25.460 --> 01:28.505
-Sometimes.
♪ Music ♪

01:28.505 --> 01:30.925
♪ I'm awesome, no you're
not dude don't lie. ♪

01:30.925 --> 01:33.677
♪ I'm awesome, I'm driving
